text: The following lists events that happened in 1930 in Iceland. ==Incumbents== *Monarch - Kristján X *Prime Minister - Tryggvi Þórhallsson ==Events== ==Births== Vigdís Finnbogadóttir, President 1980-1996 *22 March - Eythor Thorlaksson, guitarist and composer *15 April - Vigdís Finnbogadóttir, politician. *26 May - Ragnhildur Helgadóttir, politician (d. 2016). *25 August - Baldur Ragnarsson, poet ==Deaths== ==References== Category:1930s in Iceland Iceland Iceland Category:Years of the 20th century in Iceland
title: 1930 in Iceland
